responses: {"Q0":"I'm not necessarily sure I chose the correct way to think about the question but after I decided my answer for several of them, following that criteria for the rest was easy.","Q1":"I compared the largest red dot to the largest blue dot, and the second largest red dot to the second largest blue dot and so on. So I would say it was accurate if the order in size of dots was red, blue, red, blue, red, blue, etc. I also much more highly valued the comparison of the two largest dots of each color.
